{"tid":502693,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕毒拎post] 聖誕BoxingDay認真玩","createTime":"2017-12-18T07:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:38:34.000Z","uid":62225,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3efa1495f7386a68be41f3ef8462e7ab7bc5f14c","tid":502693,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"[九龍東人專屬] 搞左個活動，歡迎一齊玩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每年都會搞聖誕節活動，講真，大家應該唔會想聖誕節得1，2 個人過，聖誕節其實一玩人開下p 係最開心。<br />\n<br />\n都知道如果身邊d 朋友唔搞活動玩就永世都無野好玩，所以今年我繼續搞。不喜勿鬧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之有Party game 一齊玩，有野食一齊食，有獎一齊抽。<br />\n仲嘗試整左一個game 係一齊玩解密碼去救一個人，因為今次有地方包左個場黎玩，好多地方一齊玩，簡簡單單同大家玩一個下午。<br />\n<br />\n唔講太多，有興趣自己報名<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeB3JKQEYBK_ghy2NNvfYi07uwUxTd3pqFaaNUIiSo-RShrfQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeB3JKQEYBK_ghy2NNvfYi07uwUxTd3pqFaaNUIiSo-RShrfQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=nFksNvsqUfASnyJ%2Bh%2BiiD2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=07a78096\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeB3JKQEYBK_ghy2NNvfYi07uwUxTd3pqFaaNUIiSo-RShrfQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n認真，都要有d 野預備，希望有興趣既朋友快d 報名，我應承大家21／12前報名既朋友中獎機會一定多2倍。<br />\n<br />\n利申：少毒 (即管鬧我一定全部都係毒氣衝天既活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"7d18a0cb5a9cb60a55fd503db5d9d289350de1b3","tid":502693,"uid":4001,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"呢d party無得賺， 搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"45e142b8d360dd02711341bdd084e684a7493403","tid":502693,"uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1